Output screenshots/demo-status.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1100
Set Height 400
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

Hide
Type "alias willow=/Users/raj.joshi/code/willow/bin/willow"
Enter
Type "cd ~/.willow/worktrees/willow/main"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 300ms
Show

Type "willow status"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3s
